name: The Midnight Train
description:
One can find a high variety of methods when it comes to traversing the Tapestry.
Among them, the Midnight Train is one of the most popular.
Both vehicle and living creature, it slithers across many areas of the Tapestry, offering safe passage through its chaotic, labyrinthic and extremely dangerous landscapes.
In exchange for each travel, the dreamer must surrender himself to a night of dreamless sleep.
